State ex rel. Seabolt
v.
State Highway Patrol Retirement Sys. 2018-0695 Supreme Court of Ohio. July 9, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MEDIATION MATTERS

The following case has been returned to the regular docket under S.Ct.Prac.R. 19.01. The appellant shall file a brief within 40 days, and the parties shall otherwise proceed in accordance with S.Ct.Prac.R. 16.02 through 16.07. As provided in S.Ct.Prac.R. 16.07, the court may dismiss the case or take other action if the parties fail to timely file merit briefs.
